 class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xtf1665702608323.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xtf1665702608323.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xtf1665702608323.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xtf1665702608323\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $text\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xtf1665702608323___text_292202\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the text of a message or help text.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__topic_d90095e1_d90096e1_d90097e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__p_d90098e1_d90099e1_d90100e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__p_d90101e1_d90102e1_d90103e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vLabelText=$text(%%$fieldname)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__topic_d59962e1_d59963e1_d59964e1_d59965e1_d59966e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d852145e81\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__table_d9797e1_d9798e1_d9799e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__table_d9797e1_d9798e1_d9799e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__table_d9797e1_d9798e1_d9799e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__table_d9797e1_d9798e1_d9799e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtf1665702608323__table_d9797e1_d9798e1_d9799e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtf1665702608323__table_d9797e1_d9798e1_d9799e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtf1665702608323__table_d9797e1_d9798e1_d9799e1__entry__3\">\n Message name.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__topic_d59967e1_d59968e1_d59969e1_d59970e1_d59971e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d852145e135\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__li_d35744e1_d35745e1_d35746e1\">Text associated with the message <var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__li_d35747e1_d35748e1_d35749e1\">Text of message 8006, if the message identified by <var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var> does not exist or cannot be found.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__topic_d59972e1_d59973e1_d59974e1_d59975e1_d59976e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d852145e156\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__topic_d59977e1_d59978e1_d59979e1_d59980e1_d59981e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d852145e166\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__p_d90119e1_d90120e1_d90121e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span> is commonly used to access messages and help texts in runtime libraries.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__p_d90122e1_d90123e1_d90124e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span> uses the current language and library (in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>) to retrieve the text. If a message or help text cannot be found with the current <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>, Uniface also looks for combinations with language USA and library USYS.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__p_d90125e1_d90126e1_d90127e1\">You can use the function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$textexist</span> to determine if a message or help text exists before requesting the text with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__p_d90128e1_d90129e1_d90130e1\">If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span> is used in a component that is run on a server, it is the developer's or deployment manager's responsibility to ensure that the referenced texts are available in a UAR file.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__section_tmg_gjj_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d852145e211\">Example: Displaying Help Text </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example displays the string in the message HELPTEXT:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__pre_unv_gjj_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help\n help/noborder $text(HELPTEXT),3,4,7,23\nend; help</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">If you use a help message naming convention of <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Fieldname</var> _HLP</code>, you can use the following ProcScript\n               statement in the help trigger of the modeled field:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__pre_vnv_gjj_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help ; of field\n help $text(\"%%$fieldname%%%_HLP\")\nend; help</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">(Of course, you should not use this ProcScript in the entity-level\n               help trigger, since <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldname</span> is only valid when used in\n               field-level triggers.)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">If you are using a variable that holds IDString, the value in the\n               variable must be substituted in a string. You cannot use the variable name directly.\n               For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xtf1665702608323__pre_wnv_gjj_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vString = \"9004\"\nhelp $text(\"%%vString\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afo1665702607468.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Askmess</a><p>Specify whether the message is displayed as an askmess message.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zks1720074466587.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>help</a><p>Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ubi1665702607312.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>message</a><p>Display the specified string in the message line (if it is available), or an interactive dialog box.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ubo1665702607631.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>putmess</a><p>Append text to the message frame.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rja1665702608398.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$textexist</a><p>Return an indication of whether the specified message or help text exists.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/viq1665702608478.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger help</a><p>Trigger for reacting to the user's request for online help in a desktop application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533906\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533906\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$text Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $text Return the text of a message or help text. $text ( IDString ) Example: vLabelText=$text(%%$fieldname) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description IDString String Message name. Return Values Text associated with the message IDString . Text of message 8006, if the message identified by IDString does not exist or cannot be found. Use Allowed in all component types. Description $text is commonly used to access messages and help texts in runtime libraries. $text uses the current language and library (in $language and $variation ) to retrieve the text. If a message or help text cannot be found with the current $language and $variation , Uniface also looks for combinations with language USA and library USYS. You can use the function $textexist to determine if a message or help text exists before requesting the text with $text . If $text is used in a component that is run on a server, it is the developer's or deployment manager's responsibility to ensure that the referenced texts are available in a UAR file. Example: Displaying Help Text The following example displays the string in the message HELPTEXT: trigger help help/noborder $text(HELPTEXT),3,4,7,23 end; help Copy If you use a help message naming convention of Fieldname _HLP , you can use the following ProcScript statement in the help trigger of the modeled field: trigger help ; of field help $text(\"%%$fieldname%%%_HLP\") end; help Copy (Of course, you should not use this ProcScript in the entity-level help trigger, since $fieldname is only valid when used in field-level triggers.) If you are using a variable that holds IDString, the value in the variable must be substituted in a string. You cannot use the variable name directly. For example: vString = \"9004\" help $text(\"%%vString\") Copy Related Links Askmess Specify whether the message is displayed as an askmess message. help Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system. message Display the specified string in the message line (if it is available), or an interactive dialog box. putmess Append text to the message frame. $textexist Return an indication of whether the specified message or help text exists. trigger help Trigger for reacting to the user's request for online help in a desktop application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}